title: 21 acres of pristine nature conservancy!
posting_body: Text 9694A to my cell for more info!
Discover a sophisticated living experience at Woods apartments.
With beautiful views of Lake Austin, surrounding bluffs, and 21 acres of pristine nature conservancy, Woods is both peacefully secluded and in the middle of everything.

Conveniently located in the Westlake Area of Austin hill country and within the top-rated Eanes Independent School District, there are plenty of school, shopping, recreation, and dining options just outside your door.
Our pet-friendly one and two-bedroom open floor plans are both spacious and modern.
They feature luxury finishes such as ceramic tiling, stainless steel appliances, dark maple, hardwood cabinets, oversized walk-in closets, and a private patio or balcony.
Come home to a fully-equipped kitchen with granite countertops, full-sized washer and dryer connections, and in select floorplans, a wood-burning fireplace, double sink vanity, and garden tub.
Outside your home, our community offers a 24-hour fitness center, swimming pools, grilling areas, Wi-Fi at the pool and clubhouse, and a billiards room with Long Shuffle Board.
See what makes Woods a great place to call home and reserve your apartment online today!
